Henchman: *pant* *pant*... That was quite the heavy labor...
Does it hurt anywhere...? *pant* *pant*... Ugh, my back...

Memimi: It's not that it hurts... but isn't this... kind of
in the way...? Um... I'm not saying it's embarrassing or
anything... but isn't it a nuisance...?

Finally, Memimi was hung upside down at the entrance of the
station, spread-eagled and completely naked...

The station building at Dorietoku Station isn't very large.
Naturally, the entrance is only about two meters in height
and width. Being suspended with her lower half up means that
station users will have to pass by with her exposed crotch
right at face level, up close.

Passerby: What the hell are those guys doing...? They've
hung up a girl. And she's naked... wow...

Passerby: That's Shark Broccoli, right? The one from the
convenience store... Seems like he's become the go-to guy
for lewd stuff. Not that I'm complaining...

Memimi: (I'm getting so much attention...! Hanging like
this, I can't hide anything... and from the people behind
me... they must be getting quite the view...)

Henchman: Hehehe, with this, everyone using the station will
get an up-close look at your asshole and pussy, less than a
meter away! We took photos too, so we're heading back now.
Enjoy being stared at by the crowd!

Henchman: We'll just say this is part of the convenience
store's promotion, so don't go complaining to the onlookers!
See ya!!

Memimi: Wa... wait, don't go! Wait... Ah, they really
left... They're coming back, right...? Hey...!?

The henchmen, along with Shark Broccoli and his underlings,
had gone off somewhere... Left alone, Memimi struggled with
all her might to hold back the tears that threatened to
overflow from the intense feelings of vulnerability and
embarrassment...
